[Turkana County is a county in the former Rift Valley Province of Kenya. It is bordered by the countries of Uganda to the west; South Sudan and Ethiopia, including the disputed Ilemi Triangle, to the north and northeast; and Lake Turkana to the east. It is located in northwestern Kenya and can be seen on a map at https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turkana_County. - Mod.LL]

